nglaterra, Reino Unido","lifeSummary":"Cuando John Brockhull nació en 1320, en Lewes, Sussex, Inglaterra, su papá, Thomas Brockhull, tenía 31 años y su mamá, Joan Criol Lady of Brockhull, tenía 30 años. Se casó con Ida or Editha de Criol en 1340, en Kent, Inglaterra, Reino Unido. Fueron padres de por lo menos 1 hijo. En 1349, a la edad de 31 años, su ocupación registrada era sheriff of kent - in the time of king edward en Saltwood, Kent, Inglaterra, Reino Unido. Murió en mayo de 1383, en Saltwood, Kent, Inglaterra, a la edad de 63 años, y fue sepultado en Canterbury, Kent, Inglaterra."},"sv":{"1320–May 1383":"1320–maj 1383","1320–1383":"1320–1383","1327–1383":"1327–1383","1350–1397":"1350–1397","1290–1390":"1290–1390","1340":"1340","1350":"1350","1383":"1383","1382":"1382","1390":"1390","16 May 1382":"16 maj 1382","1290":"1290","liv. abt. 1380":"omkring 1380","1327":"1327","Abt 1350":"omkring 1350","1337":"1337","May 1383":"maj 1383","1453":"1453","1320":"1320","1397":"1397","1328":"1328","Lewes, Sussex, England":"Lewes, Sussex, England","Hythe, Kent, England":"Hythe, Kent, England","England":"England, United Kingdom","Church of Friars Minors, Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, England","Brockhull, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, England, United Kingdom","Brockhill Manor, Saltwood, Kent, England":"Saltwood, Kent, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England, United Kingdom","Walmer, Kent, England":"Walmer, Kent, England, United Kingdom"},"tl":{"1320–May 1383":"1320–Mayo 1383","1320–1383":"1320–1383","1327–1383":"1327–1383","1350–1397":"1350–1397","1290–1390":"1290–1390","1340":"1340","1350":"1350","1383":"1383","1382":"1382","1390":"1390","16 May 1382":"ika-16 ng Mayo 1382","1290":"1290","liv. abt. 1380":"mga 1380","1327":"1327","Abt 1350":"mga 1350","1337":"1337","May 1383":"Mayo 1383","1453":"1453","1320":"1320","1397":"1397","1328":"1328","Lewes, Sussex, England":"Lewes, Sussex, England","Hythe, Kent, England":"Hythe, Kent, England","England":"Eng